title: Scenic, Le Paysage a Chasses, ca. 1970
description: Modern printing from woodblocks after the 1831 design by Deltil. The colored scenic is composed of 4 scenes: Stag hunting, wild fowling, hare and partridge shooting, and wild boar hunting.

tombstone.epitaph: Scenic, Le Paysage a Chasses, ca. 1970; Manufactured by Zuber & Cie (France); France; block printed on machine-made paper; L x W: 228 × 50 cm (7 ft. 5 3/4 in. × 19 11/16 in.); Gift of A.L. Diament & Co.; 1974-40-1-1/32
